=== 選角 ===
2012年10月22日，宣布[[雪琳·伍德莉|雪琳·伍德莉]]將飾演女主角{{link-en|分歧者角色列表|List of The Divergent trilogy characters#Beatrice "Tris" Prior|碧翠絲·「翠絲」·普里爾}}<ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.j-14.com/posts/shailene-woodley-talks-divergent-movie-casting-5968 |title= Shailene Woodley Talks 'Divergent' Movie Casting |accessdate= 2013-06-08 |archive-date= 2017-09-06 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20170906133558/http://www.j-14.com/posts/shailene-woodley-talks-divergent-movie-casting-5968 |dead-url= no }}</ref>。2013年3月15日，[[席歐·詹姆斯|席歐·詹姆斯]]確認演出男主角{{link-en|分歧者角色列表|List of The Divergent trilogy characters#Tobias "Four" Eaton|托比亞‧「四號」·伊頓}}<ref name="ew-four">{{cite journal|url=http://insidemovies.ew.com/2013/03/15/divergent-four-theo-james/|title='Divergent' has found its 'Four'! Theo James talks about starring in the next big YA franchise|accessdate=2013-06-08|journal=|archive-date=2015-01-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150111065023/http://insidemovies.ew.com/2013/03/15/divergent-four-theo-james/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，[[盧卡斯·提爾|盧卡斯·提爾]]、[[傑克·雷諾|傑克·雷諾]]、[[傑瑞米·爾文|傑瑞米·爾文]]、[[亞歷克斯·帕蒂弗|亞歷克斯·帕蒂弗]]、[[布蘭頓·思懷茲|布蘭頓·思懷茲]]、[[亞歷山大·路德韋格|亞歷山大·路德韋格]]以及[[路克·布萊西|路克·布萊西]]都曾被認定為該角色的演員人選<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.deadline.com/2012/11/who-has-divergent-chemistry-with-shailene-woodley/|title=Who Has 'Divergent' Chemistry With Shailene Woodley?|accessdate=2013-06-08|archive-date=2014-06-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140613123048/http://www.deadline.com/2012/11/who-has-divergent-chemistry-with-shailene-woodley/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/jack-reynor-lands-starring-role-409850|title=Jack Reynor Lands Starring Role in 'Transformers 4'|accessdate=2013-06-08|work=The Hollywood Reporter|first=Borys|last=Kit|archive-date=2014-10-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141012134652/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/jack-reynor-lands-starring-role-409850|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

